reviews.text:
An assortments of foodstuff but taste pretty much the same.
One item I personally liked was the minced beef congee.  Only reason we come here is because my wife and kids like the food and the price is very reasonable for the size of the dishes.
價錢貴，人多，餐牌都不怎麼改的
粥是用槳煑的，很快就變成水。麵也煑得太耐，不夠爽。
用自助售賣機有糖水送， 超值。
食品錯，員工有禮貌，但價錢稍貴和食品種類少。
